reviews.name: Ascension St. John Nowata

reviews_data.review_text: If I could have done zero stars I would have! I was very upset with the care my son received here. The lady who answered the phone was rude, one of the nurses(I didn’t  catch her name) was rude, the doctor that seen my son had disgusting hands, dirt all in his finger nails and didn’t have the audacity to even wear gloves!! I will not be stepping foot into this location nor will I recommend my family to go here!! They didn’t even give me an exact diagnosis, immediately walked into the room and said well idk what that is, sorry I can’t give you an answer, told me I would have to figure it out.
reviews_data.owner_answer: We understand your frustration and would sincerely like to give this situation the time and attention you deserve. May we ask that you please call us at 918-331-1217 (Mon-Fri 8 am-4:30 pm) so that we can address your concerns? Thank you. -Ascension St. John Community Manager
